    "Turn off stamping if your organisation records hours only via manual entries \u2014 the punch clock disappears for all employees." : "Sl\u00e5 stempling fra, hvis din organisation kun registrerer timer via manuelle indtastninger - punch-uret forsvinder for alle medarbejdere.",
    "Turning this off hides the project picker everywhere and stops you from linking new hours to a project. Projects you already linked stay linked until a manager changes them. Projects with per-person pricing only appear if you are on the project team." : "Hvis du sl\u00e5r dette fra, skjules projektv\u00e6lgeren overalt og forhindrer dig i at linke nye timer til et projekt. Projekter, du allerede har linket, forbliver knyttet, indtil en leder \u00e6ndrer dem. Projekter med pris pr. person vises kun, hvis du er i projektteamet.",
