    "Type: %1$s" : "Type: %1$s",
    "Typical number of work days each week for this model (e.g. 4 for a four-day week). Used for model-based vacation entitlement calculations." : "Typisk antal arbejdsdage hver uge for denne model (f.eks. 4 for en fire-dages uge). Anvendes til modelbaserede ferieberegninger.",
    "Typical value in Germany: 31 March (month 3, day 31). If that day does not exist in a month (e.g. 31 February), the last day of that month is used automatically." : "Typisk v\u00e6rdi i Tyskland: 31. marts (31. m\u00e5ned, dag 31). Hvis den dag ikke eksisterer i en m\u00e5ned (f.eks. 31. februar), bruges den sidste dag i den m\u00e5ned automatisk.",
